          {
            "turoyo": ") u=rabo d-i=qriṯo moṣele u=ahl d-u=bayt-ayḏe ḥatta d-maḥṣən at=tarʕe d-nošo d-lo ʕobər ‘",
            "translations": [
              "Der Dorfvorsteher wies seine Familie an, die Türen fest zu verrammeln, damit niemand hereinkäme"
            ],
            "references": [
              "25/24"
            ]
          },
          {
            "turoyo": "[MT]; bəṯṯər məd-yaqər u=kewo aʕle, qrele l-ann=abn-ayḏe, l-u=ahl diḏe, l-an=noše d-kət-wo-le, mawṣele aw=waṣiyat diḏe",
            "translations": [
              "‘Als seine Krankheit schwer geworden war, rief er seine Söhne, seine Familie, die Leute, die er hatte, und gab ihnen seinen letzten Willen kund’; 26/7 [LTN] [MT];"
            ],
            "references": []
          },
          {
            "turoyo": "moṣele d-mḥaḏ̣árral-le səsyo w-sayfo w-rumḥo, w-mǧahazle b-u=slāḥ",
            "translations": [
              "he left instructions for them to prepare a horse, a sword and a lance for him, and equiped him with a weapon"
            ],
            "references": []
          },
          {
            "turoyo": "Mawseli ʕal u abrayḏi dlo gonaw.",
            "translations": [],
            "references": [
              "İlyas p.c",
              "2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "turoyo": ") elo, Silo maḥatle išara ʕal ab=bote d-ap=pəsmam-ayḏe, moṣele i=ʕaskar d-nošo lə=mqaru laf-elayye",
            "translations": [
              "But Silo marked his cousins’ houses and commanded the army not to near them"
            ],
            "references": []
          },
          {
            "turoyo": "Mawṣele l moran la talmiḏayḏe dәzzehәn lu ġlilo",
            "translations": [],
            "references": [
              "İlyas p.c"
            ]
          }
        ],
